quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,1,(alr) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  10,2,"akan amrana ejbana lilnaas 'inzalna alwhy bialquran ealaa rajul minhum yndhrhm eiqab allh, wybshshir aladhin amanuu biallah warusulih 'ana lahum ajrana hsnana bima qddamu min salih alaemal? falamaa 'atahum rasul allah salaa allah ealayh wasalam bwhy allah wtlah elyhm, qal almnkrwn: 'inn mhmdana sahr, wama ja' bih sihr zahir albtlan"
  10,3,"'iina rabakum allah aladhi awjd alsmwat wal'ard fi sitat ayam, thuma astwa -ay eala wartfe- ealaa alearsh astwa' ylyq bjlalh wezmth, yudabir 'umur khlqh, la ydadduh fi qdayh ahd, wala yashfae eindah shafe yawm alqiamat 'iilaa min baed 'an yadhan lah balshfaet, faebuduu allah rabakum almtsf bhdhh alsfat, wa'akhlasuu lah alebad. 'afala ttezwn wtetbrwn bhdhh alayat walhjj?"
  10,4,"'ila rabukum meadkm yawm alqiamat jmyeana, whdha waead allah alhq, hu aldhy yabda 'iijad alkhalq thuma yueiduh baed almwt, fywjdh hyana khyyth alawla, liajzi man saddaq allah wrswlh, waeamil al'aemal alhasanat 'ahsan aljaza' baledl. waladhin jahaduu whdanyt allah wrsalt rasulih lahum sharab min maa' shadid alhararat yashwi alwujuh wyqttie alamea', walahum eadhab mwje bsbb kufruhum wdlalhm"
  10,5,"allh hu aladhi jaeal alshams dya', wajaeal alqamar nwrana, wqddar alqamar mnazl, fbalshms taerif alayam, wbalqmr taerif alshuhur walaewam, ma khalaq allah taealaa alshams walqamar 'iilaa lhkmt ezymt, wdlalt ealaa kamal qudrat allah welmh, ybyin alhujaj waladlt liqawm yaelamun alhikmat fi 'iibdae alkhlq"
  10,6,"'in fi teaqb allayl walnahar wama khalaq allah fi alsmwat wal'ard min eajayib alkhalq wama fihima min 'iibdae wnzam, ladlt whjjana wadihatan liqawm yakhshawn eiqab allah wskhth wedhabh"